data.name: Journal_NavigateBrowserFailed

data.comment: This is emitted to attached debuggers to provide diagnostic information. The String.Format method is used to provide exception details in place of the '{0}' portion of the message.

data.value: The UriFragmentHelper is unable to navigate to the Uri fragment provided because doing so would violate the maximum Uri length restriction of 2048 characters.
